1
00:00:00,646 --> 00:00:04,996
Are you doing the football pools, Brain?
Brain,你正在下足球赛的赌注吗?

2
00:00:05,072 --> 00:00:08,463
Yes, I've nearly finished, Julie.
是的.我就要弄完了,Julie.

3
00:00:09,098 --> 00:00:12,724
I'm sure we'll win something this week.
我敢肯定这星期我们会赢点什么的.

4
00:00:13,012 --> 00:00:18,875
You always say that, but we never win anything!
你老是那样说,但是我们从来没赢过!

5
00:00:19,142 --> 00:00:23,738
What will you do if you win a lot of money?
要是你赢了许多钱,你会做什么呢?

6
00:00:23,882 --> 00:00:29,830
If I win a lot of money I'll buy you a mink coat!
要是我赢了许多钱,我给你买件貂皮大衣.

7
00:00:29,831 --> 00:00:33,244
I don't want a mink coat!
我不想要貂皮大衣.

8
00:00:33,245 --> 00:00:36,697
I want to see the world.
我想去看看世界.

9
00:00:36,811 --> 00:00:41,322
All right. If we win a lot of money,
好的.要是我们赢了很多钱,

10
00:00:41,323 --> 00:00:47,689
We'll travel round the world and we'll stay at the best hotels.
我们就去周游世界,并且住最好的旅馆.

11
00:00:48,186 --> 00:00:54,114
Then we'll return home and buy a big house in the country.
然后我们返回家园,在乡下买幢大房子.

12
00:00:54,115 --> 00:00:58,048
We'll have a beautiful garden and ...
我们将有一个漂亮的花园和……

13
00:00:58,370 --> 00:01:03,859
But if we spend all that money we'll be poor again.
但是如果我们把所有那些钱都花光了,我们又会变穷的.

14
00:01:03,860 --> 00:01:06,425
What'll we do then?
那时我们怎么办呢?

15
00:01:07,045 --> 00:01:13,306
If we spend all the money,we'll try and win the football pools again.
如果我们花光了所有钱,我们设法在足球赛赌注上再赢一次.

16
00:01:13,351 --> 00:01:20,146
It's a pleasant dream but everything depends on 'if'!
这是个美好的梦,但一切都取决于“如果”!

